title: Free Food
content: There are free food tables set up at GFS. Will be here 9am-5pm tues, weds and thurs. Stop by as needed.

title: Pop Up Vaccine Event for People Experiencing Homelessness
content: For Minnesotans who work with homeless members of the community: Pop Up Vaccine Event for People Experiencing Homelessness. DAY: Friday, March 26th. TIME: 10 am – 4 pm. The one dose Janssen (J&J) vaccine will be provided. A collaboration between Health Care for the Homeless and Hennepin Healthcare, and in partnership with Avivo street outreach, St. Stephen’s street outreach, American Indian Task Force (AITF) and American Indian Movement (AIM).
contact: All Nations Indian Church Parking Lot, 1515 E 23rd Street, Mpls, MN 55404
